v1data <- function(data)
{
    out <- as_tibble(read.table(data))%>%select(-V1)%>%
        `colnames<-`(v1names)
    return(out)
}

cor2plot <- function(data, title)
{
    cor.data <- round(cor(data), 1)
    ggcorrplot(cor.data, 
               type='lower', 
               lab=TRUE, 
               ## lab_size=5, 
               ## outline.color='white', 
               colors=RColorBrewer::brewer.pal(n=3, name='Greys'),
               title=title,
               p.mat=cor_pmat(cor.data), 
               insig='blank', 
               ggtheme=theme(
                   plot.title=element_text(size=16, face='bold'), 
                   axis.text.x=element_text(size=15), 
                   axis.text.y=element_text(size=15), 
                   axis.title.x=element_blank(),
                   axis.title.y=element_blank(),
                   panel.background=element_blank(),
                   axis.ticks=element_blank(),
                   legend.justification=c(1, 0),
                   legend.position=c(0.4, 0.85),
                   legend.direction='horizontal',
                   legend.title=element_blank(),
                   legend.text=element_text(size=11)))+
        scale_x_discrete(labels=c(expression(beta[2]),
                                  expression(gamma[1]),
                                  expression(gamma[2]),
                                  expression(w[1]),
                                  expression(w[2]),
                                  expression(log(sigma[1]^2)),
                                  expression(log(sigma[2]^2)),
                                  expression(z(rho[12]))))+
        scale_y_discrete(labels=c(expression(beta[1]), 
                                  expression(beta[2]),
                                  expression(gamma[1]),
                                  expression(gamma[2]),
                                  expression(w[1]),
                                  expression(w[2]),
                                  expression(log(sigma[1]^2)),
                                  expression(log(sigma[2]^2))))+
        coord_cartesian()
}

true1 <- c( 3,  2.6, 2.5, 4, 5, 10, log(1), log(0.6), atanh(0.1))
true2 <- c(-2, -1.5, 1, 1.5, 3,  4, log(1), log(0.6), atanh(0.1))

cerror <- function(coefs, true)
{
    error <- coefs
    for (i in seq(ncol(coefs))) { error[i] <- true[i]-coefs[i] }
    out <- error%>%
        summarize_all(mean)%>%
        add_row(error%>%summarize_all(quantile, c(0.025, 0.975)))%>%
        mutate(label=c('mean', 'q025', 'q975'))%>%
        pivot_longer(!label, names_to='par', values_to='value')%>%
        pivot_wider(names_from=label, values_from=value)
    out$par <- as_factor(out$par)
    return(out)
}
ev1_cs1_1 <- cerror(v1_cs1_1[1:9], true1)
ev1_cs1_2 <- cerror(v1_cs1_2[1:9], true2)
ev1_cs2_1 <- cerror(v1_cs2_1[1:9], true1)
ev1_cs2_2 <- cerror(v1_cs2_2[1:9], true2)
ev1_cs3_1 <- cerror(v1_cs3_1[1:9], true1)
ev1_cs3_2 <- cerror(v1_cs3_2[1:9], true2)

bias2plot <- function(data, title)
{
    ggplot(data, aes(ymin=q025, ymax=q975, x=par))+
        geom_linerange(
            color=RColorBrewer::brewer.pal(n=3, name='Greys')[2],
            position=position_dodge(width=0.2),
            size=3)+
        ## ylim(c(-1, 1))+
        geom_point(mapping=aes(x=par, y=mean), size=2)+
        geom_hline(yintercept=0, linetype='dashed')+
        labs(x=NULL, y='Bias',
             title=title, subtitle='with 2.5% and 97.5% quantiles')+
        scale_x_discrete(labels=c(expression(beta[1]),
                                  expression(beta[2]),
                                  expression(gamma[1]),
                                  expression(gamma[2]),
                                  expression(w[1]),
                                  expression(w[2]),
                                  expression(log(sigma[1]^2)),
                                  expression(log(sigma[2]^2)),
                                  expression(z(rho[12]))))+
        coord_flip()+
        theme_minimal()+
        theme(plot.title=element_text(size=12, face='bold'),
              plot.subtitle=element_text(size=11, face='italic'),
              axis.text.x=element_text(size=11),
              axis.text.y=element_text(size=11),
              axis.title.x=element_text(
                  size=12, 
                  margin=unit(c(t=3, r=0, b=0, l=0), 'mm')))
}

p1 <- bias2plot(ev1_cs1_1, title='v1_cs1_1 parameters bias')

beta1 <- c(
    true1[1],
    mean(v1_cs1_1$beta1), mean(v1_cs2_1$beta1), mean(v1_cs3_1$beta1), 
    true2[1],
    mean(v1_cs1_2$beta1), mean(v1_cs2_2$beta1), mean(v1_cs3_2$beta1)
)
beta2 <- c(
    true1[2],
    mean(v1_cs1_1$beta2), mean(v1_cs2_1$beta2), mean(v1_cs3_1$beta2), 
    true2[2],
    mean(v1_cs1_2$beta2), mean(v1_cs2_2$beta2), mean(v1_cs3_2$beta2)
)
gamma1 <- c(
    true1[3],
    mean(v1_cs1_1$gama1), mean(v1_cs2_1$gama1), mean(v1_cs3_1$gama1), 
    true2[3],
    mean(v1_cs1_2$gama1), mean(v1_cs2_2$gama1), mean(v1_cs3_2$gama1)
)
gamma2 <- c(
    true1[4],
    mean(v1_cs1_1$gama2), mean(v1_cs2_1$gama2), mean(v1_cs3_1$gama2), 
    true2[4],
    mean(v1_cs1_2$gama2), mean(v1_cs2_2$gama2), mean(v1_cs3_2$gama2)
)
w1 <- c(
    true1[5], mean(v1_cs1_1$w1), mean(v1_cs2_1$w1), mean(v1_cs3_1$w1), 
    true2[5], mean(v1_cs1_2$w1), mean(v1_cs2_2$w1), mean(v1_cs3_2$w1)
)
w2 <- c(
    true1[6], mean(v1_cs1_1$w2), mean(v1_cs2_1$w2), mean(v1_cs3_1$w2), 
    true2[6], mean(v1_cs1_2$w2), mean(v1_cs2_2$w2), mean(v1_cs3_2$w2)
)
t     <- seq(30, 79.9, length.out=100)
delta <- 80
size  <- length(beta1)
nt    <- length(t)

cif1 <- vector(mode='list', length=size)
cif2 <- vector(mode='list', length=size)
for (i in seq(size)) {
    risklevel1 <- exp(beta1[i])
    risklevel2 <- exp(beta2[i])
    mlog1 <- risklevel1/(1+risklevel1+risklevel2)
    mlog2 <- risklevel2/(1+risklevel1+risklevel2)
    trajectory1 <- pnorm(w1[i]*atanh(2*t/delta-1)-gamma1[i])
    trajectory2 <- pnorm(w2[i]*atanh(2*t/delta-1)-gamma2[i])
    cif1[[i]] <- mlog1*trajectory1
    cif2[[i]] <- mlog2*trajectory2
}
model <- as_factor(c(
    rep('v1true_1', nt),
    rep('v1_cs1_1', nt), rep('v1_cs2_1', nt), rep('v1_cs3_1', nt),
    rep('v1true_2', nt),
    rep('v1_cs1_2', nt), rep('v1_cs2_2', nt), rep('v1_cs3_2', nt)
))

data_cif <- tibble(curve=c(rep('CIF: Cause 1', 8*nt),
                           rep('CIF: Cause 2', 8*nt)), 
                   model=rep(model, 2),
                   type=rep(c(rep('Configuration 1', 4*nt),
                              rep('Configuration 2', 4*nt)),
                            2),
                   value=c(unlist(cif1), unlist(cif2)),
                   time=rep(t, 2*8))

ggplot(data_cif, aes(x=time, y=value, group=model))+
    geom_line(aes(linetype=model))+
    facet_wrap(~curve+type)+
    labs(x='Time', y=NULL, linetype='Model')+
    theme_minimal()+
    theme(axis.title.x=element_text(
              size=12,
              margin=unit(c(t=3, r=0, b=0, l=0), 'mm')),
          axis.text.x=element_text(size=11), 
          axis.text.y=element_text(size=11), 
          legend.position=c(0.1, 0.8),
          legend.text=element_text(size=12),
          legend.title=element_blank(), 
          legend.box.background=element_rect(color='black'), 
          strip.background=element_rect(colour='black', fill='white'),
          strip.text.x=element_text(size=12))

plotS <- function(S, title)
{
    longS <- reshape2::melt(S, na.rm=TRUE)
    longS$Var1 <- as_factor(longS$Var1)
    longS$Var2 <- fct_relevel(as_factor(longS$Var2), rev)
    ggplot(longS, aes(x=Var1, y=Var2, fill=value))+
        geom_tile(color='black', size=0.5)+
        geom_text(aes(label=round(value, 5)), size=4.5)+
        scale_fill_gradient(low='white', high='white')+
        labs(title=title)+
        scale_x_discrete(labels=c(expression(u[1]), 
                                  expression(u[2])))+
        scale_y_discrete(labels=c(expression(u[2]),
                                  expression(u[1])))+
        theme_minimal()+
        theme(axis.text.x=element_text(size=12, color='black'),
              axis.text.y=element_text(size=12, color='black'), 
              axis.title.x=element_blank(), 
              axis.title.y=element_blank(),
              panel.grid.major=element_blank(),
              legend.position='none',
              plot.title=element_text(size=12, face='bold'))
}
